  • SABSA
  • 4+1
  • Dragon1

}
{ Syracom Enterprise Architecture Method (SEAM)

  The SEAM framework tries to structure the EAM capability of an organization.

  Conception areas:
    • Strategy
    • Method
    • Organization
    • Delivarable
    • Tool
}
